<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.7">
<l>parataṉum tampi catturuk kaṉaṉṉu milakkuma ṉōṭumai tiliyu</l>
<l>miravunaṉ pakalun tuticeyya niṉṟa virāvaṇān takaṉai yemmāṉai</l>
<l>kuravamē kamaḻuṅ kuḷirppoḻi lūṭu kuyiloṭu mayilkaṇiṉ ṟāla</l>
<l>viraviyiṉ katirkaḷ nuḻaitalcey taṟiyāt tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our lord, the one who caused Rāvaṇa’s end, who endures</l>
<l rend="indent">so that night and midday</l>
<l>Bharata and [his] younger brother Śatrughna, along with Lakśmaṇa,</l>
<l rend="indent">and Maitili perform praises,</l>
<l>I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi where, in the midst of cool groves</l>
<l rend="indent">scented by bottleflowers,</l>
<l>As cuckoos and peacocks call, the creeping of the sun’s rays is unknown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
